name: Touch It / Technologic

wikiText:
"Touch It / Technologic" is the second track of thirteen on Daft Punk's, 'Alive 2007' album.
 
 The album is a recording from multiple locations of their Alive 2007 world tour which debuted out of Bercy.
 
 The track is a mash-up of their tracks "Technologic" and "Oh Yeah"  and a  sample of Busta Rhymes' "Touch It."
